reviews.review_text: Pretty clean and new place. The decorations on the walls are also pretty cool. Ordered sundaes for my kids using mobile app and the service prompt. I wish there were more softer seating like a sofa but it is pretty spacious with a lot of seating. The play place is also good. The seating could be improved as there is lot of open space but seating is cramped on one side. Would like to go there again as my kids liked it.

The girls here are always so friendly and supportive so it s my favourite place to stop by on night shifts! Shout out to the manager and staff member serving me early morning 4am on august 23rd, they made my whole day during a busy shift!

I had the pleasure of being served by Reshma and Japneet at McDonalds, and I must say they truly exemplify exceptional customer service. Their sweet and generous demeanor made my visit incredibly enjoyable. Their attentiveness and kindness went above and beyond, creating a positive and welcoming atmosphere. Their dedication to ensuring a delightful dining experience is truly commendable. Kudos to Reshma, Japneet and the team for their outstanding service!
